comments: Williamson (NOP) makes marginal contact with Bazley (OKC) in the post.
Horford (OKC) makes incidental contact to Adams' (NOP) arm after the release that does not affect his shot attempt.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) delivers contact to Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) prior to gathering the ball during his drive towards the basket.
Ball (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dort (OKC) and absorbs the contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes clean contact to the ball while defending Ingram (NOP) on the perimeter.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Ingram (NOP).
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) releases from Ball (NOP) at the end of his drive.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) draws Ball (NOP) into the air towards him and the contact results in a foul on Ball (NOP) even if contact is initiated by Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Adams (NOP) makes marginal contact with Dort (OKC) during the pick.
Williamson (NOP) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Horford (OKC) makes marginal contact to Williamson's (NOP) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Ball (NOP) moves laterally along Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and the contact is marginal during his drive.
Adams (NOP) brushes Horford's (OKC) arm during the rebound.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) makes clean contact to the ball after Horford (OKC) secures the loose ball.
Horford (OKC) makes incidental contact with Alexander-Walker (NOP) upon grabbing the rebound.
Ball (NOP) extends his arm and makes contact to Hill's (OKC) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adams (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bazley (OKC) and absorbs the contact.
Ingram (NOP) releases from Dort (OKC) at the end of his drive.
Adams (NOP) engages and disengages with Horford (OKC) during the rebound.
Horford (OKC) makes clean contact to the ball as he deflects the loose ball away from Adams (NOP).
